{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Local Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #2a9d8f; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e9c46a 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        #about, #portfolio, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about h2, #portfolio h2, #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #2a9d8f; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        #about p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: auto;\n        }\n        .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            color: #2a9d8f; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        .portfolio-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: auto;\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            background: #2a9d8f; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: 0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background: #268a80; /* Slightly darker blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        a {\n            color: #2a9d8f; /* Brand blue */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        a:hover {\n            color: #268a80;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n            <p>Exploring Creativity Through [Art Medium]</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to my portfolio! I am a local artist passionate about [briefly describe your artistic focus, e.g., capturing the beauty of nature, abstract expressionism, vibrant portraits]. My work aims to evoke [emotion or idea, e.g., a sense of wonder, introspection, joy] through the use of [mention techniques or styles, e.g., bold colors, delicate brushstrokes, mixed media].</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Portfolio</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 1</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 2</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 3</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 4</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+5\" alt=\"Artwork 5\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 5</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2a9d8f/ffffff?text=Artwork+6\" alt=\"Artwork 6\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 6</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact</h2>\n            <p>Interested in a commission or have questions? Feel free to reach out!</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}